<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Lorenz Gottsmann zu Büg</head><p>Der Rat bittet, die Armleute der Christine von Wildenstein, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, zu sichern.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_515" id="257r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_515_r1l1">Laurencʒ Gocʒman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l2">cʒu der Püge </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_515_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Gocʒman / vvir bıten euch <expan>fleiſʒıklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ Jr eʒ fürbaʒ gen fraun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l5">Criſtein der wıldenſteinerin 
<add><ab facs="#facs_515_line_1576349499582_4078"> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin </ab></add> vnd den Jren <expan>beſcheydenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> halten 
<del rend="strikethrough">wo </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l6">vnd ır ſchonen vvöllet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wıllen / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc bıſʒ das mit </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_line_1576349532010_4094">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>freuntlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> rehten auſʒgetr </del> / Alſo daʒ ſie vnd ~ das 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Jren </del> Jr vor ew vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l10">den ewren 
<add><ab facs="#facs_515_r1l9">hinfür </ab></add> ſicher ſein 
<del rend="strikethrough">bıʒ dıe ſache mit <expan>freuntlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> rehten </del> das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l11">vvir gern v̈mb euch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan></del> vnd lat vns des ewr <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l12"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıder wiſſen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Egıdij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_515" id="257r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Laurencz Goczman czu der Püge</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Goczman, wir biten euch
                                <expan>fleisziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir ez fürbaz gen fraun
                        Cristein, der Wildensteinerin, <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                            burgerin</add>, und den iren <expan>bescheydenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        halten und ir schonen wöllet durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen,
                        also daz sie und das ir vor ew und den ewren <add>hinfür</add> sicher sein.
                        Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir gern ümb euch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> und lat uns des ewr
                                <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
